---
// 파일 위치: src/pages/en/index.astro
import BaseHead from '../../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
    </head>
    <body>
        <Header />
        <main>
            <h1>🍻 Brewage Bear 🐼</h1>
            <p>
                I record the phenomena encountered within the endless cycle of software engineering in my own words.<br/>
                In a world devoid of eternal answers, endurance is in itself a meaningful creation and a rebellion against the absurd.
            </p>
            <p>
                This space is not a gallery for neatly polished "perfect answers."<br/>
                Rather, it is the transparent trajectory of a struggle—willingly embracing despair to break through a single problem, and fiercely persisting, much like rolling the boulder up the mountain once again.
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong><a href="/en/posts/">Blog</a></strong>: The complete archive of my technical records and struggles.</li>
                <li><strong><a href="/en/tags/">Tags</a></strong>: Scattered writings and thoughts, categorized by key interests.</li>
            </ul>        
            <p>
                Should you have any thoughts or feedback while reading, please feel free to leave a comment at the bottom of the post.
            </p>
            <p>
                👉 <a href="/en/posts/">Go to the English Blog</a>
            </p>
        </main>
        <Footer />
    </body>
</html>